Momozono Nanami, a high school girl, has just become a deity.
Though some things are better left unexplained,
to put it simply, being a deity is not for everyone.
And now we present, the second episode!
My father ran away, I got evicted from my house...
Then I got lost, and some guy gave me his house.
When I went, it turned out to be a rundown temple.
And then they kept saying I was the Earth Deity.
Then a really rude demon named Tomoe said that he would not accept it,
except I ended up kissing that thing and now he is my familiar.
You already did that last episode.
The inner sanctuary of the shrine.
But it is completely different from yesterday.
I remember it looking like it was going to fall apart.
Tomoe-dono gathered all of this for you
so that you could live more comfortably!
Last night, you finally took Tomoe-dono as your familiar!
It is a familiar's duty to serve his deity!
I forced a kiss on Tomoe last night!
at your side for quite some time.
I forced him into being my familiar...
Your bedroom was quite a mess,
so I cleaned up while you slept.
I did what I could think of.
While it was against my will, from here on out, I am your familiar.
I, Tomoe, am mandated to carry out your orders without qualm should our eyes meet.
Should you be troubled by anything, do not hesitate to come to me.
I thought you would be more upset about becoming my familiar.
You do not seem upset at all!
It would be half-assed of me to be simply upset.
I am so pissed off, you could not possibly begin to understand!
Why on earth do I have to serve some wretch like you?!
It is so damn pathetic that I could not get a wink of sleep last night!
But what is done is done.
I will simply have to make you into a deity worthy of my service.
Deities have an innate power within them.
You measure the standing of a deity...
by how much of this power they can use.
you first have to listen to people's prayers.
Simply granting their wishes will be a quick and easy way to do this.
For example, Mikage was a deity of marriage.
Having listened to many prayers for marriage, his power to grant such wishes is very strong.
So this temple is for good fortune in marriage?
He is taking the time to explain everything clearly even though he does not like me...
Now, let us see how powerful you are.
You may use a talisman if you like.
Oh, this thing I used before, huh?
All right, time to show him what I can do!
We cannot take care of this place alone!
I had not noticed until now,
but Tomoe's doing everything, like the bedroom, the meals, the cleaning, pretty much everything.
Our beloved idol Kurama-san has, of all places, transferred to Uchigami High!
Where are you going to in such a rush?
I just remembered that I have to train my powers!
I have to get to school!
Going to school and hanging out with my girlfriends while squealing over celebrities...
That is where the real me lives!
This is my chance to meet Kurama Shinjirou.
Nanami-chan, allow me to tell him.
Kurama is a mega-celebrity who is taking the nation and its girls by storm.
Sporting black wings, his persona is that of a fallen angel.
That said, his profile says that he is a character shrouded in mystery.
And he is at my school right now!
Even if I hang around, it is not like we will get any prayers.
You should know that there will be demons out to get you.
This mark tells them that you are an Earth Deity.
Keep in mind that you are just a powerless girl.
You going out is like begging to be eaten.
I am up to my ears in chores here!
You should do your fair share!
If you want to go that badly, I guess you can.
I finally come back to school and this is what I get!
What is on your head, Momozono?
I heard that you would finally come back to school and you walk in with that!
Why do I have to be in the same class as you again, Isobe?
Wear this hood to hide your forehead.
I stick out like a sore thumb!
I got to get this on photo.
Black wings that shine even in
the blackest depths of the night.
That girl who lost her home.
did a human just bully you?
I was worried, so I came to check up on you.
Kurama said something horrible to me.
It is all because you made me wear this hood!
Now that you have met that Kurama guy, you do not have a reason to come to school anymore, right?
Let us go back to the shrine.
I am standing here crying, and you have the nerve to smile?
You do not care about me, do you?
Were you crying in the bathroom?
I was just a bit irritated.
Every day, the kids at school look at me like I am some kind of exotic animal.
Sorry I took it out on you.
Do not let it get to you.
I do not actually hate you.
If that is the case, then I deserved it.
I gawked at you just like everyone else.
I will not ever look at you again, so goodbye.
I did not know Kurama was that kind of person!
I feel like an idiot for going out of my way to meet him with this hood on.
I feel so bad for Nanami-sama.
She does not deserve to be bullied by Tomoe-dono and end up like that!
Hold on, I was not bullying her.
What kind of cheap-ass food did you bring for lunch today?
It is not like you forgot it at home or anything, right?
I-I am going to get bread today!
Do you even have enough money to buy bread?
What do you take me for?
I cannot possibly have this much!
Well, I guess 30,000 is pocket change.
Momozono-san, where did you get that money?
You do not think she stole it, do you?
I gave that money to her.
I remember her saying that she did not have enough money to buy bread.
What is he going on about?
Nanami-sama, I humbly apologize for my tardiness.
Today is your first day on the job, a because for celebration.
I, Tomoe, have attempted to craft an exquisite lunch for you.
Also, I have a few words for everyone.
Nanami-sama is an important master to us.
I, Tomoe, will not tolerate any words of slander or actions against her.
That money you could not find, as you can see, is right on the floor.
I remember specifically putting that cash in her pocket!
As for everyone else, I humbly ask for your generosity toward Nanami-sama.
The only person in the whole world...
Nanami-chan just experienced one heck of a start to her school days.
Let us fast-forward to her second day!
You are forgetting this masterfully crafted triple lunch box and this cat hood to which I have attached a seasonal flower.
Sorry, I think I will go without the hood today!
I am only going to school.
Walking out without the hood is much like walking onto a battlefield naked.
You should not talk like that until you can protect yourself.
I will just have one section of the lunch box.
Phew, it is a relief to get that thing off my head!
If he is, could you introduce him to us?
Oh, I brought lunch today, so I do not think he is coming.
Or maybe because I am so popular
No, because I do not like you.
Who does she think she is?!
Celebrities are a pain in the ass.
All she had to do was wear the hood.
Now I have to watch over her all day.
I have not even cooked dinner.
I suppose salt-roasted sweet fish will suffice for tonight.
I have to cook dinner and babysit this girl.
Is this part of what familiars do too?
I almost miss my past life.
The kind of life that would make anyone's skin crawl.
Why did you call me out here, Kurama?
Let me ask you this first.
Any other girl would avert their eyes and blush the instant our eyes meet,
so why do you say you do not like me?
I covered for you yesterday, and I even apologized.
I do not get what there is not to like about me.
If you want, I will even consider becoming your
What did you just call me?!
If you keep talking down to people like that, forget about getting a girl, you will not even make friends.
If you have no other business, I am leaving.
I do not care for any of them.
All I want is you, Earth Deity.
If I can have you, then I will...
What is this chill down my spine?
You must be pretty sharp to set your sights on Nanami this soon.
You are the familiar from yesterday!
I am the Crow Goblin of Mt. Kura.
It is been sixteen years since I descended from those mountains.
Now that you have seen my true identity...
How do you like that, fox?
I heard your services are fantastic.
If I become the Earth Deity, I would not mind making you my familiar!
You would rather have me over that girl, right?
You think you can become a deity?
All I need is a bite of that girl's heart.
When I think of how people like you want to become a deity...
it makes me giddy to know that Nanami is my current deity.
Ostrich meat is low in calories and rich in nutrients and minerals.
You wanted to become an Earth Deity, right?
If Nanami eats you, you can become one with meat on her butt.
Allow me to try my hand at making you into an Earth Deity.
We are having whole-roasted ostrich for dinner tonight.
Why is there an ostrich running around?
How the hell is he a familiar?!
I cannot hold back these feelings.
Oh, I am so happy for you, Lisa!
You can live happily ever after with Mike!
I wish my high school years could be like this too!
I heard there is an ostrich being chased by a fireball!
What is that supposed to mean?
Not seriously injuring anybody does not make it okay!
You have got some nerve going on a rampage around my school!
And why is Kurama a bird now?
That man is not a human.
He is a demon, a crow goblin to be exact.
You are not a fallen angel from hell?!
W-Well, turn him back into a human for now.
I will let you off the hook this time, so do not because me trouble, and do not be mean to me.
I-I-I-I thought I was going to die!
Let us clean it up first.
An idol cannot walk around with cut on his face.
I do not particularly like you, but there are tons of others that do.
You have to at least take care of your looks.
Otherwise, you are just insulting them.
Wait, why did I get the lecture while he gets his wounds tended to?!
That is because you are not injured, Tomoe!
That is only because I can take care of myself!
Why are you even at school in the first place?
Nanami-san, I see you are becoming a good deity.
You are not walking out without your hood tomorrow!
Next Episode, a priestess appears at the residence of the Earth Deity!
She is fallen in love with a human?
Can love really blossom between ghouls and humans?
Next time, The Deity Ties Fate!
